---
title: Sequence Diagram Test — actors, messages, notes, activations, loops
---
%% Exercises Mermaid sequence diagram constructs: actor declarations with multi-line
%% participants, sync and async messages, self-messages, activations, notes spanning
%% participants, and a loop with an alt branch. The bake script was designed for
%% flowcharts — this file is the regression test for whether sequence diagrams need
%% their own pass set.
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant GE as Gemini<br/>Enterprise
    participant AE as Agent<br/>Engine
    participant CR as Cloud<br/>Run

    U->>GE: Ask a question
    activate GE
    GE->>AE: Forward to brain
    activate AE
    Note over AE: Process and<br/>plan tool call
    AE->>CR: POST /tool
    activate CR
    CR->>CR: Run tool logic
    CR-->>AE: HTTP 200 JSON
    deactivate CR
    loop until satisfied
        AE->>CR: Refine
        activate CR
        CR-->>AE: Result
        deactivate CR
    end
    alt success
        AE-->>GE: Final answer
    else error
        AE-->>GE: Error message
    end
    deactivate AE
    GE-->>U: Response
    deactivate GE
